{"id":171267,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201189/","date":"2011-08-10T01:00:28Z","modified":"2011-08-10T01:00:28Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/9","content":"<p><p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【美国国债降级</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">】</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904140604576496553310745950.html?mod=googlenews_wsj\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国难题：迁怒于美国但是却被困在美国国债</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/09/business/global/chinese-fault-beijings-moves-on-foreign-reserves.html?_r=2\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国民众指责政府的外汇储备策略</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——周末，中国互联网上充满了批评之声，中国网民指责政府未能合理管理巨量外汇贮备</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。(已有初译，正在校对)</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基和平基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45289&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+CarnegieEndowmentForInternationalPeaceGeneralPublicationsAndEvents+(DC+-+General+Publications+and+Events)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国的债务危机至少可以缓解中美两国在贸易和汇率上的紧</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">张</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">黄育空）</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/08/trouble_in_triple_a_world?page=full\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">三</span>A<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国家的麻烦：其他国家的信誉值真的牢不可摧？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——还有法国、英国、加拿大、德国和卢森堡都可以看看他们的负</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">债</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">全球之声：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/08/china-taxi-drivers-and-railway-workers-on-strike/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">综合了微博上对杭州出租车司机和铁路工人的罢工消息</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基和平基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/2011/07/29/wenzhou-crash-shows-dangers-of-china-s-nuclear-power-ambitions/4knz\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">温州撞车为中国的核跃进敲响了警钟</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/opinions/editorials/canadas-diplomats-teach-china-a-lesson-in-due-process/article2123129/?utm_medium=Feeds:%20RSS/Atom\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加拿大外交官给中国上课，什么是正当司法程序</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加大使馆在微博上贴出赖昌星判决书</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度</span></span><span><span>Rediff </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.rediff.com/news/column/us-seeks-consulate-in-tibet-china-fumes/20110808.htm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">想要</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">开</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">设</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">拉萨领事馆，中国不满</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美参议院外交委员会指示国务院，不允许中国在美国开设新的领事馆，除非美国获准开设拉萨领馆</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基和平基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45292&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+CarnegieEndowmentForInternationalPeaceGeneralPublicationsAndEvents+(DC+-+General+Publications+and+Events)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国可能避开硬着陆，但是正奔向债务危</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">机</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span></span><span><span>Michael Pettis</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《亚洲时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.atimes.com/atimes/China/MH10Ad01.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一系列由海外学者、外交官签名给马英九的公开信批评台湾的司法不公正等问题，让马疲于招架</span></a></span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">但是信件公开的时间让人怀疑和选举有关</span></span><span><span> </span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《亚洲时报》</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.atimes.com/atimes/South_Asia/MH10Df02.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">维族激进分子威胁了中巴关系</span></a> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——北京批评最近在新疆发生的暴力事件中的暴徒是在巴基斯坦受训</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的</span>。</span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">辛迪加项目：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.project-syndicate.org/commentary/chellaney19/English\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度学者：中国的民族问题成为大麻烦</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国陈旧的民族政策看来对维稳已经难起重大作</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">用</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基和平基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45291&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+CarnegieEndowmentForInternationalPeaceGeneralPublicationsAndEvents+(DC+-+General+Publications+and+Events)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中产阶级冲突</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——即将到来的并非</span></span><span><span>“</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">文明的冲突</span></span><span><span>”</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，而是未能满足预期的中产阶级冲突，他们在富裕国家陷入衰退，在发展中国家蓬勃兴起，但他们的预期都可能落空</span></span><span><span> &#8230;</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《亚洲时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Korea/MH10Dg02.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北韩新富的秘密世界</span></a> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——官员们可能通过非法手段致富；而普通的北韩百姓也通过外贸同时付钱给官员而手头宽裕；街头出现了寿司店和啤酒屋</span></span><span><span>&#8230;</span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-09/syria-pressed-to-end-crackdown-as-arab-states-join-criticism.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阿拉伯国家加入批评叙利亚的队列，要求其停止镇压民众</span></a></span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/europe/08/09/uk.riots/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">伦敦一名</span>29<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁男子被射杀，结果导致了席卷全英的骚乱</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——周二，紧张局势持续，警察和暴徒对峙</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：【图说】</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/08/london_burning?page=full\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">燃烧的伦敦</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span></span><span><span>14</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">图</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：周一，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/africa/08/08/libya.war/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">利比亚反政府军称，他们仍然控制着离的黎波里最近的重镇贝尔盖纳姆</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，尽管战事仍在城东继</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">续</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/08/revolutions_end?page=full\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">革命</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">结</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">局</span></a> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从苏联解体</span></span><span><span>20</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年后的角度看今天的阿拉伯之春</span></span><span><span> </span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110809/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_inflation\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span>7<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月通胀创下</span>37<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月来的新高</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国领导人面临压力，要在当前美欧债务危机中，保持经济增长，同时降低生活成本</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-09/china-6-5-inflation-limits-policy-response-to-global-crisis.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span>6.5%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的通胀率限制了它对全球危机的应对手</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">段</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>BBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-14455664\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对通胀的担心可能加剧中国的不稳</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">定</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span></span><span><span>1:41</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的视频</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></span><sub><span></span></sub></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/BUSINESS/08/09/global.economy/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲早盘暴跌</span>5%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，下午止跌回</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">升</span></a></span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：【图说】</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/08/all_the_worlds_traders_and_all_the_worlds_yen?page=full\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">全球股市狂跌</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span></span><span><span>15</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">图）——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">垂头丧气的各地股票交易员</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">们</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-09/tepco-reports-572-billion-yen-loss-says-no-chance-of-insolvency.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东电本季度亏损</span>5720<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万亿日元，用于清理设备和赔偿受害</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-09/yahoo-investors-sue-over-alibaba-restructuring-of-payment-system.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">股民起诉雅虎误导支付宝重组信</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">息</span></a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-08/hay-sent-to-china-cheaper-roiling-u-s-dairies-freight-markets.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">把美国干草出口到中国比运到加州中部还要便宜，推高美国奶业价格</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；个中缘由耐人寻味</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span>CNET</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.cnet.com/8301-27076_3-20089648-248/report-fake-apple-stores-being-forced-to-cover-up/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国调查伪苹果店</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——下令不得使用苹果标志，从外部装修上去掉苹果品牌</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><s